data.description: Schedule your appointment today! MLS#20522396 – Altura built home, Lamar elementary school, in the Jackson Run subdivision just off Interstate 30, in Greenville. A very desirable area and proximity to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Greenville is a fast-growing community with a small-town feel. Making this a wonderful place for your family to call home! This single-story home includes durable tile flooring, granite countertops and many luxury features. Come experience the quality of life you can only find here!
